text: Jean Jaillard (6 October 1931 - 12 November 2009) was a French gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:2009 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Carpentras
